::KitKat::

She smiled, "You know, those two are so dence that light bends around then." 
She laughed.  She picked up another rock, threw it and shot it.  It wasn't a 
live bot, but it did help pass the time.

"How about dense and denser?"
She stood up, trandformed into wolf mode and sat back down nest to 
Quickstrike.  She felt better being in beast mode.  She chuckled.
"You know, if those two were half as good as they said they were, both of us 
would be in trouble. But somehow, I think they might work out yet."
